.png", "id": "1128214698348100", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39031333_1128214701681433_6540732684018521630_n.png?_nc_cat=101&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=lPu3B4D3ayoQ7kNvgErVAN4&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYBSRT3DNdTeEE61xnY4l8mphi4w6jFF2v5Jdou8mNpdVQ&oe=66E5655E"}, {"file_name": "Ruzosc5.png", "id": "252247994490318", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39001663_252247997823651_1579156496494017132_n.png?_nc_cat=108&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=n9GuMQ5G-tYQ7kNvgE7VHy1&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYANUfYfV7Y_a-DeMjIlskomTA_AnoQGSeBgpCjf1dMUjw&oe=66E58492"}], "video_trailer": null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": {"file_name": "BG_02.png", "id": "755258066122271", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/75462961_755258069455604_3152224420084855536_n.png?_nc_cat=103&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=ipHOBSyxjK4Q7kNvgFRc9lq&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYCgJ91vlwHtmSB-FmB-lXy_LH2spQ-HEkrJm3CUj_kvwA&oe=66E5784E"}, "display_name": "Ruzo", "keywords": [], "long_description": "VR Game for adventure seekers.\nRuzo, a young boy passionate about hunting, dreams of becoming a skilled hunter like the elders in his village. Village relies on the sacred forest for their livelihood, but Ruzo is restricted from venturing deep until he completes his training.\n\nUnexpectedly, a mysterious force plagues the nearby forest, causing suffering to the villagers. Desperate for a solution, Ruzo steps up, he decides to explore the depths of the forest.\n\nWill he be able to save his dying village????\n\nThe game unfolds as Ruzo evolves from a curious boy into an unexpected hero, facing suspenseful encounters and unravelling mysteries in the haunting forest.", "short_description": "VR shooting Game."}]}, "developer_name": "Mindpixels", "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://www.mindpixels.io/privacy-policy/#developer", "developer_terms_of_service_url": null, "publisher_name": "Mindpixels", "support_website_url": null,